Abstract
With the rise of the Internet and technology, Online Social Networks (OSNs) turned into challenging cases of study. 
Analyzing and mining social network enhances the understanding of the relationships among people
and to help address several issues regarding society. One such analysis area is Influence Analysis.
It requires the analysis of links between users
which can be easily performed using Graph Database. Neo4j Graph Database enables
us to treat relationships between data as equally important as the data it-
self and study the connection between users. It provides user friendly visualization of the
result.

Keywords - OSN, Neo4j, SNA, Cypher.
